Style Sheet (style.css)

/* Styles go here */

h1 {
  color: #7828a3;
  text-decoration: underline;
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 70px;
  font-family: 'Chela One', cursive;
  background-image: url("https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQtQiCnWr_HgmZ5084ch1xP2d0BcQBpWPfSD9TTYFHhtmznc7_4Tw");
  padding: 50px;
}

      /*The CSS below allows me to center the two images in the same line.  Neat, right?!?!*/

.centerTwoImages {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
}


      /*The CSS below provides space between the two images.  We will learn more about this in the upcoming days.*/
      
img {
  margin-left: 100px;
  margin-right: 100px;
}

h4 {
  font-size: 30px;
  text-align: center;
  color:#a02121;
}
